<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Yeah, what Karol66 said.  To enter a keep (controlled by your realm) a gatekeeper actually casts a teleport spell on you and puts you inside.  This is not the same thing as 'Zoning' where you see the loading screen.<P>Unfortunately, pets can't zone with you.  When you zone into a new area you lose your pet.<P>I should have mentioned that if there isn't an object, NPC or PC available to target for the "Go To Target" command, you can always select yourself to accomplish the same thing.<P>--------------------<P>Admin - Level 50 Sorcerer - Kay<BR>Breeto - Level 47 Armsman - Kay
