<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
<STRONG>- To make a pet enter a keep with you, port into the keep via the gatekeeper, once inside, target a player or object inside the keep and click "Go To Target".</STRONG><P>I keep seeing ppl post this to target something else like a merchant or guard.  Why not just target <B>yourself</B> and GO TO TARGET.  It works.   <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0"><P>edit: ACK, Breeto beat me to it. Oh well. Shoulda read all the way through first.<P>--------------------<P>Frazier - 49 Briton Sorc
